    "Tables 14 and 15 show examples of how we preprocessed the text of the privacy policies as described in Section 4.3; more concretely, for the topic modeling analysis.",
    "In the English example below, company names and an email address were replaced with the placeholders \"COMPANYNAME\" and \"REPLACEDMAIL, \" respectively.",
    "In the German example on the next page, additionally a URL was replaced with \"REPLACEDURL. \"",
    "The white spaces before and after the placeholders are put intentionally to prevent accidental concatenation of words with punctuation or placeholders.",
    "They do not cause any problems with text processing."
  ],
